Insatllling Node:
Selecting node package from url: http://nodejs.org/dist/
  wget http://nodejs.org/dist/v8.11.1/node-v8.11.1-linux-x64.tar.gz
Untar the file 
  sudo tar --strip-components 1 -xzvf node-v* -C /usr/local
Checking node version
